Last season the Northern Iowa women's basketball team's season ended with a home game in the WNIT. This season UNI head women's Tanya Warren believes the sky or NCAA tournament is the limit...The Panthers made the big dance in 2010 and 2011. 
This season the Panthers return four starters including senior forward Jen Keitel who missed much of last season..
